text: Diego Rosende Lagos (born 11 February 1986) is a Chilean footballer. Rosende played as a defender for Universidad Católica, Coquimbo Unido, Palestino and currently plays for Magallanes. ==Honours== ===Club=== ;Universidad Católica * Primera División de Chile (2): 2005 Clausura, 2010 ;Palestino *Copa Chile (1): 2018 ==References== * Profile at BDFA Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Chilean footballers Category:Unión Española footballers Category:Club Deportivo Universidad Católica footballers Category:Deportes La Serena footballers Category:Coquimbo Unido footballers Category:Club Deportivo Palestino footballers Category:Chilean Primera División players Category:Colegio del Verbo Divino alumni Category:Association football defenders Category:Association football midfielders
